708133f-a.text:
1)Jacob Ruppert's Brewery; bottling department, one of the oldest buildings, N.E. corner of Third Avenue and 90th Street. Mr. Ruppert, in addition to his brewing activities, is owner of the New York Yankees, a professional baseball club in the
American League.
June 26, 1931.
P.L.Sperr. Photographer.

2) Bottling department, Jacob Ruppert's Brewery, N.E. corner of
Third Avenue and 90th Street.
June 26, 1931.
P.L.Sperr, Photographer.
